I"‚	<p>The <code>voicerss</code> text-to-speech platform uses <a href="http://www.voicerss.org/">VoiceRSS</a> Text-to-Speech engine to read a text with natural sounding voices.</p>
<h2>Configuration</h2>
<p>To enable text-to-speech with VoiceRSS, add the following lines to your <code>configuration.yaml</code>:</p>
<pre><code class="language-yaml"># Example configuration.yaml entry
tts:
  - platform: voicerss
    api_key: YOUR_API_KEY
</code></pre>
<div class="config-vars">
  <h3><a class="title-link" name="configuration-variables" href="#configuration-variables"></a> Configuration Variables</h3>
  <dl class=''><dt><a class='title-link' name='api_key' href='#api_key'></a> api_key</dt><dd><p class='desc'><span class='type'>(<span class='string'>string</span>)</span><span class='required'>(Required)</span><span class='description'><p>The API Key for VoiceRSS.</p>
</span></p></dd><dt><a class='title-link' name='language' href='#language'></a> language</dt><dd><p class='desc'><span class='type'>(<span class='string'>string</span>)</span><span class='required'>(Optional)</span><span class='description'><p>The language to use.</p>
</span></p><p class='default'>
Default value: <p><code>en-us</code></p>
</p></dd><dt><a class='title-link' name='codec' href='#codec'></a> codec</dt><dd><p class='desc'><span class='type'>(<span class='string'>string</span>)</span><span class='required'>(Optional)</span><span class='description'><p>The audio codec.</p>
</span></p><p class='default'>
Default value: <p>mp3</p>
</p></dd><dt><a class='title-link' name='format' href='#format'></a> format</dt><dd><p class='desc'><span class='type'>(<span class='string'>string</span>)</span><span class='required'>(Optional)</span><span class='description'><p>The audio sample format.</p>
</span></p><p class='default'>
Default value: <p>8khz_8bit_mono</p>
</p></dd></dl>
</div>
<p>Check the <a href="http://www.voicerss.org/api/documentation.aspx">VoiceRSS API documentation</a> for allowed values.</p>
<h2>Full configuration example</h2>
<p>The configuration sample below shows how an entry can look like:</p>
<pre><code class="language-yaml"># Example configuration.yaml entry
tts:
  - platform: voicerss
    api_key: YOUR_API_KEY
    language: 'de-de'
    codec: mp3
    format: '8khz_8bit_mono'
</code></pre>
<p>Please note, some media_players require a certain format. For example the Sonos requires a format of â€˜44khz_16bit_stereoâ€™</p>
